===================================
The GGZ Gaming Zone - Documentation
===================================

This module contains reference documentation, tutorials and help for game
module writers. The client/server specification and a general overview are also
included, as well as game comparison tables and the guides for hosting and game
development.

Some documents are also published online, and may be updated from time to time.
Consult the following pages for more up-to-date information:
	http://www.ggzgamingzone.org/docs/

Have fun!
	- The GGZ Gaming Zone Development Team

